00:45:03.860 --> 00:45:08.309
of work. We're going over the fonts that are
currently in the directory, and we're commissioning

00:45:08.309 --> 00:45:14.660
new fonts. We're doing a lot of work to improve
the quality of Windows rendering. It's not

00:45:14.660 --> 00:45:18.940
really just Windows 7. It's all versions of
Windows that have two rendering engines. There's

00:45:18.940 --> 00:45:24.839
GDI, and then there's the new rendering engine
that's used, among other places, by Internet

00:45:24.839 --> 00:45:29.740
Explorer 9. And the new rendering engine is
actually capable of a lot better quality.

00:45:29.740 --> 00:45:34.400
