00:53:20.980 --> 00:53:27.289
only works a little bit or only works in some
cases. So we're really trying to make the

00:53:27.289 --> 00:53:33.849
support for that 100% rock solid before we
roll it out. But it is definitely important

00:53:33.849 --> 00:53:39.260
for Google to make these fonts worldwide,
all languages. And so that's what we're working

00:53:39.260 --> 00:53:40.380
on.
